294
00:14:49,000 --> 00:14:49,400
Where is it?

295
00:14:49,960 --> 00:14:51,360
Under Lord Li's yard

296
00:14:51,560 --> 00:14:53,040
Lanting and Mo Chou have gone to dig

297
00:14:53,160 --> 00:14:54,360
Once they dig out the money

298
00:14:54,520 --> 00:14:55,480
