299
00:14:55,600 --> 00:14:56,400
If you have evidence, you can do it.

300
00:14:56,400 --> 00:14:56,960
No.

301
00:14:57,720 --> 00:14:58,440
This is a trap.

302
00:14:59,680 --> 00:15:01,080
