314
00:15:25,880 --> 00:15:26,520
Changhao!

315
00:15:26,840 --> 00:15:27,640
Who is he?

316
00:15:28,560 --> 00:15:29,480
You're the prince.

317
00:15:29,760 --> 00:15:30,640
to come here, right?

318
00:15:30,880 --> 00:15:32,080
