333
00:17:04,240 --> 00:17:05,240
I'm your wife.

334
00:17:06,040 --> 00:17:06,920
I'll be wherever you are.

335
00:17:07,200 --> 00:17:07,920
I'm not leaving anyway.

336
00:17:10,040 --> 00:17:11,119
I won't let you get hurt.

337
00:17:11,640 --> 00:17:11,960
Let's go.

338
00:17:15,160 --> 00:17:15,720
This way.

339
00:17:18,640 --> 00:17:20,480
