340
00:17:22,640 --> 00:17:24,640
A prince like him

341
00:17:25,119 --> 00:17:26,200
is ignorant,

342
00:17:26,640 --> 00:17:28,079
and willful.

343
00:17:29,040 --> 00:17:30,800
