350
00:17:55,320 --> 00:17:56,360
and framed the Liang family.

351
00:17:57,280 --> 00:17:58,760
He should be executed.

352
00:17:58,800 --> 00:18:00,120
You should pay with your life. Your Majesty.

353
00:18:21,640 --> 00:18:22,400
Ning Ji!

354
00:18:23,080 --> 00:18:23,760
Are you okay?

355
00:18:23,880 --> 00:18:24,800
