356
00:18:25,240 --> 00:18:26,280
Du Ruofei is right.

357
00:18:27,400 --> 00:18:28,440
We have a common goal.

358
00:18:29,920 --> 00:18:30,600
What about Changhao?

359
00:18:31,520 --> 00:18:32,760
I've sent someone to save him.

360
00:18:32,840 --> 00:18:34,160
He should be able to meet us soon.

361
00:18:34,320 --> 00:18:34,760
Okay

362
00:18:54,280 --> 00:18:55,200
Here we go. Here we go.

363
00:18:56,480 --> 00:18:57,760
You're here, after all.

364
00:18:58,000 --> 00:18:59,160
We haven't avenged yet.

365
00:18:59,840 --> 00:19:01,000
Why don't you give it a go?

366
00:19:01,440 --> 00:19:03,160
You have to be capable to take revenge.

367
00:19:13,760 --> 00:19:15,720
Wang, you bastard!

368
00:19:23,080 --> 00:19:24,000
Everyone is here.

369
00:19:25,480 --> 00:19:27,360
It saves me a lot of trouble.

370
00:19:28,240 --> 00:19:28,880
Today,

371
00:19:29,760 --> 00:19:31,440
none of you can leave.
